com.symantec.dlpx.flexresponse.action

Interface ActionResult


  • public interface ActionResult
    An ActionResult is returned by when an action is executed. It is intended to be used solely by the plugin runtime. A plugin action creates an ActionResult using ActionResultBuilder.
    See Also:
    IncidentResponseAction.execute(com.symantec.dlpx.flexresponse.incident.Incident, com.symantec.dlpx.flexresponse.configuration.ConfigurationParameters), ActionResultBuilder
